text: One Love is a 2003 Jamaican Norwegian British romance movie directed by Rick Elgood and Don Letts and stars Ky-Mani Marley, Cherine Anderson, Vas Blackwood, Idris Elba. == Other websites == * Category:2003 romance movies Category:Jamaican movies Category:Norwegian movies Category:British romance movies
